The,W,C,Selection,API,is,a,specification,for,an,API,that,provides,selection,related,functionality,It,allows,authors,and,users,to,select,a,portion,of,a,document,or,to,specify,a,range,of,content,for,copy,paste,and,other,editing,operations,This,API,specification,is,based,on,the,HTML,Editing,API,specification